  <brief_title>SA4503 8-Week Study in Major Depressive Disorder (MDD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase II, Multi-Centre, Randomized, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Parallel Group Study to Determine the Safety and Efficacy of Treatment With SA4503, Once Daily for 8 Weeks, in Subjects With Major Depressive Disorder</official_title>
