  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the efficacy of SA4503 compared to placebo in the
      treatment of subjects with major depressive disorder (MDD). Secondary, to evaluate the safety
      of SA4503 compared to placebo in subjects with MDD.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
